00:00:44.990 --> 00:00:47.620
conformist, and the tendency
for us to do that much more

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:49.220
than we imagine we would.

00:00:49.220 --> 00:00:50.630
And the experimental
evidence is pretty

00:00:50.630 --> 00:00:52.290
powerful, that is true.

00:00:52.290 --> 00:00:54.430
You could call that the dark
