00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:10.540
impressions of others,
those are more

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:11.890
everyday kinds of things.

00:01:11.890 --> 00:01:13.990
But you'll see how they populate
our lives, how we

00:01:13.990 --> 00:01:16.900
think about ourselves, how we
think about people in everyday

00:01:16.900 --> 00:01:20.970
interactions, impressions
of others.

00:01:20.970 --> 00:01:22.760
We've talked a little bit,
