00:50:09.220 --> 00:50:10.220
the absolute task.

00:50:10.220 --> 00:50:12.120
There's more activation, working
harder, to do the

00:50:12.120 --> 00:50:13.190
absolute task.

00:50:13.190 --> 00:50:15.750
And for people from the United
States, working harder to do

00:50:15.750 --> 00:50:17.720
the relative task.

00:50:17.720 --> 00:50:19.480
It's not that you
can't see both.

00:50:19.480 --> 00:50:21.040
As you sit there, you understand
what a relative

00:50:21.040 --> 00:50:23.370
size and what an absolute
size is.

00:50:23.370 --> 00:50:26.670
It's just harder to take the
